cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.HC 

The paper deals with computer vision and machine learning techniques for 3D face shape and pose estimation, which falls under the scope of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The proposed method also involves the use of neural networks, which is a popular topic in computer graphics (cs.GR). The paper also mentions the use of 3D Morphable Models (3DMM), which is a common technique in multimedia (cs.MM) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC) research.
